嚟</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1761734/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1761734/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑製造派錢假象 <blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/dA8N0Lx.png\" /></blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>不如幫幫白鴿黨裝修 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>11年同15年屌人民力量同熱血公民票<br />\n今日就鳩沙田友既票<br />\n咁就送左席比民賤聯<br />\n道歉Sorry好撚假囉<br />\n人地議席就無左咩都無<br />\n你地今次就大勝食咁多議席<br />\n仲要好多區比你地逼到退選讓路含淚投<br />\n<br />\n既然你地食人血饅頭食得咁開心<br />\n手足陣間不如發夢去是旦一個白鴿黨既辦事署裝下修<br />\n反正你地今次賺咁多經費咁多人工<br />\n比2條路你地揀<br />\n裝修/捐一半人工做抗爭基金<br />\n就係咁</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>新口號同洗腦金句！想贏既入嚟同我宣傳出去 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>將香港人 反抗<br />\n變做<br />\n香港人 返工<br />\n成個口號幾撚震撼</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>保護休班警,你我有責 - #4</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔好搞休班警<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實借運動識女溝女有咩問題 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>CCtai班友仔做咩咁敏感<br />\n大家都係有相同興趣同諗法<br />\n傾得埋再交換contact上埋床有咩問題<br />\nCCTai班小朋友真係大驚小怪</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"0a8aeffe2d35eb65034417fb3c0c279cf64adfa1","tid":2040640,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"100萬買起佢真係流流地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定唔止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7464437cfd66e6d923284a25f3c6dbb000b15d17","tid":2040640,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8aeffe2d35eb65034417fb3c0c279cf64adfa1","tid":2040640,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"100萬買起佢真係流流地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定唔止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"100日圓就差唔多"},{"pid":"8e936ccfb4bf978c01603e0436f0607e0c2f6ca0","tid":2040640,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfe12722b6469b45c06b4cfa811f23cebc83efdc","tid":2040640,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"身份又唔知<br />\n連佢背景佢係咩人我地都唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先唔講佢背景未有任何值得信賴既地方<br />\n先頭既言論既可信性<br />\n先頭話有人用100萬買起佢<br />\n證據？fc左未？邊班人買起佢？仲有佢點知？成件事疑點多到<br />\n<br />\n先唔講平時佢既計劃又空泛無針對性<br />\n國民區議會？有咩用依家區議會贏左so what<br />\n去東歐去北歐搞咩姐妹城市？究竟有咩用同做緊咩<br />\n登報好有用？世界變得咁快幾日就無人記得啦<br />\n國際遊說？都成年了外國仲係含人民幣含到好爽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越諗越覺得攬炒巴（團隊）<br />\n好似早排cctai堆法師風水師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每隔幾個月叫人籌百幾萬美金<br />\n成條數唔透明<br />\n又唔知你係咪真係做<br />\n成效又有咩<br />\n大佬你買股買波馬投資都有期望回報架啦<br />\n<br />\n真係唔明咁多疑點<br />\n成個團隊咁無用<br />\n都唔知入錢比錢佢做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"e2e3e1d6b765504522b92da6d2f91b0b77ebbf29","tid":2040640,"uid":259988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能"},{"pid":"c4b22165b7bf5124807b4198acec22424586276d","tid":2040640,"uid":249639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:31:26.000Z","msg":"佢哋做嘅嘢要花幾多功夫同時間<br />\n同你咁坐喺度打幾個字就話諗深咗一層<br />\n不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"9dcef49ad5b4bb38641b144dc33c6ffe04e97301","tid":2040640,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"低級五毛狗"},{"pid":"03fd556581e1f92e6a40bc2791ee2539ffd2769e","tid":2040640,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5683bf9ffdf271939b56a99fa9d01fffdae2af3f","tid":2040640,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7464437cfd66e6d923284a25f3c6dbb000b15d17","tid":2040640,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8aeffe2d35eb65034417fb3c0c279cf64adfa1","tid":2040640,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"100萬買起佢真係流流地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定唔止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl